               <p>Come and listen to our local handbell ringers in All Saints' Hall, Onslow Gardens, CR2 9AB. Free entry, retiring collection, Refreshments of tea and cake will be provided.</p>
              </td>
              <td class="events"><%= link_to image_tag("handbell_concert.png", alt: "Handbell poster"), "resource/handbell_concert_poster.pdf" %>
              </td>
