            <tr>
              <td class="events">
                <h3><a class="anchor" id="top" name="running"></a>Jubilee Running, 10k Fun Run. Sunday 2nd July, starting at 9.30 am</h3>
                <p>Runners and walkers welcome. A slightly undulating 10k multi-terrain course encompassing the local areas of Selsdon, Sanderstead and Warlingham.</p>
                <p>Entrants must be 15 years of age. Entrance fees: UKA Affiliated Runner £10.00, Non-Affiliated Runner (Please add a further £2.00 for Race Day entry, subject to availability). Proceeds go to the British Heart foundation.</p>
                <p>For an entry form, please contact the Jubilee Church office on
                020 8651 2807, e-mail office@croydon-Jubilee.co.uk or enquire in person at Race HQ: Selsdon Hall, 132 Addington Road, Selsdon CR2 8LA</p>
